{
  "chunk_id": 3,
  "start_offset": 3590.0,
  "segments": [
    {
      "idx": 0,
      "start": 3590.005,
      "end": 3590.051,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "谁说李白就今天只能按董宇辉所说的解读出勇气呢？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start": 3590.051,
      "end": 3590.063,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "对吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start": 3590.063,
      "end": 3590.129,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那我们可以解读出很多的东西，完全看你自己怎么理解，只要大量的去了解事实，在了解事实的基础上去进行的各种的理性感性的发挥，我认为都合理。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start": 3590.129,
      "end": 3590.194,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以这可能是一个当老师的职业毛病啊，总喜欢在屏幕前絮絮叨叨，啰啰嗦嗦。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start": 3590.194,
      "end": 3590.264,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但是我特别害怕大家就是又把所有的时间从原来的游戏，从原来虚拟的东西最后全部转成了，比如说在这里听董宇辉絮叨。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start": 3590.264,
      "end": 3590.274,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "其实董宇辉絮叨的也并不对。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start": 3590.274,
      "end": 3590.286,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "董宇辉经常会说错。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start": 3590.286,
      "end": 3590.315,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "董宇辉前两天讲苏东坡的时候，然后一直脑子里想着杜甫。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "start": 3590.315,
      "end": 3590.332,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "还有人把那个视频发给我，对吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "start": 3590.332,
      "end": 3590.36,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "还有人董宇辉你写scattered stars，少写了一个E。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 10,
      "start": 3590.36,
      "end": 3590.375,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他们给我截图，发现确实是对的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 11,
      "start": 3590.375,
      "end": 3590.389,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我感谢他，我说感谢你提醒。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 3590.399,
      "end": 3590.424,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "看上一段时间就让孩子回归现实世界里，看一看书，好吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 3590.424,
      "end": 3590.49,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就像我，就像我当时在这个当年的先先的方方，资助那个孩子一样。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 3590.49,
      "end": 3590.533,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那个孩子后来考上大学之后，他一开始给我发消息，后来我说孩子你不要给我发消息了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 3590.533,
      "end": 3590.583,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你你未来是要去看更多的风景，去遇见更多有趣的人，然后呢，你要成为自己。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 3590.583,
      "end": 3591.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我只是陪伴你走一段路的人。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 17,
      "start": 3591.01,
      "end": 3591.033,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我不应该一直陪在你身边。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 18,
      "start": 3591.033,
      "end": 3591.053,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果你一直跟在我身边，说明你没有长进。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 19,
      "start": 3591.053,
      "end": 3591.063,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "对吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 20,
      "start": 3591.063,
      "end": 3591.086,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你应该像小鸟离开鸟巢一样。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 21,
      "start": 3591.1,
      "end": 3591.114,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那样离开我。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 22,
      "start": 3591.114,
      "end": 3591.143,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以那个孩子后来，我觉得他的状态就很好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 23,
      "start": 3591.143,
      "end": 3591.176,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果一个老师总希望孩子一直留在自己身边，那是一种自私。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 24,
      "start": 3591.185,
      "end": 3591.214,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "这种观点我反正我觉得我是这么想的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 25,
      "start": 3591.214,
      "end": 3591.246,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "去年我们在一开始带货的时候，有一个媒体还采访过我，说董老师你不是教过50万学生吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 26,
      "start": 3591.246,
      "end": 3591.284,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那你直播的时候随便叫上5万人，其实直播间应该人很多了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 27,
      "start": 3591.284,
      "end": 3591.304,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以大能里为什么有时候直播间三四十万人，我觉得其实很正常。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 28,
      "start": 3591.304,
      "end": 3591.323,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你光我自己的学生，真的有50万。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 29,
      "start": 3591.334,
      "end": 3591.348,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我说我从来不会允许我的学生来。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 30,
      "start": 3591.357,
      "end": 3591.424,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有一次我记得我们一开始在直播的时候，那会直播间里十几个，折腾一晚上9块9的东西卖不出去的时候，当时真的很灰心丧气。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 31,
      "start": 3591.424,
      "end": 3591.444,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我甚至都动过那样的邪念。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 32,
      "start": 3591.453,
      "end": 3591.467,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后就是说让学生来听。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 33,
      "start": 3591.467,
      "end": 3591.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但是有一天我正在直播，直播间有个学生说，董老帅，董老帅。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 34,
      "start": 3591.5,
      "end": 3591.513,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我不是董老师吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 35,
      "start": 3591.521,
      "end": 3591.527,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "老师吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 36,
      "start": 3591.527,
      "end": 3591.545,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我说去掉那一横，把我叫董老帅。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 37,
      "start": 3591.545,
      "end": 3591.554,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "自恋嘛。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 38,
      "start": 3591.554,
      "end": 3591.574,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "骗学生我是中关村朱建伦。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.85,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 39,
      "start": 3591.574,
      "end": 3591.587,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "虽然他们也不信。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 40,
      "start": 3591.587,
      "end": 3592.01,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后有一天我正在直播，我看到屏幕有个董老帅，我当时瞬间就感觉很后悔。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 41,
      "start": 3592.01,
      "end": 3592.083,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我说我知道屏幕前，你在这里，孩子手机放下，现在跟我写作业去，现在跟我读书去，现在出去打羽毛球去，现在跟我睡觉去，实在不行你跟我谈个恋爱去。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 42,
      "start": 3592.083,
      "end": 3592.094,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你记得吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 43,
      "start": 3592.094,
      "end": 3592.115,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "当时应该是我跟你打，还是我跟石明在打？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 44,
      "start": 3592.115,
      "end": 3592.12,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我忘了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 45,
      "start": 3592.12,
      "end": 3592.127,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "咱俩打。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 46,
      "start": 3592.127,
      "end": 3592.154,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我当时那天我就很生气，我突然觉得我在屏幕前失态了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 47,
      "start": 3592.154,
      "end": 3592.203,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "后来我就在我所有以前的那些学生的群里，和我发朋友圈里就提醒孩子，我说你以后不要来听了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 48,
      "start": 3592.203,
      "end": 3592.227,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你那么小，你的时间和精力不应该在我这。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 49,
      "start": 3592.233,
      "end": 3592.284,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果我因为要挣那一点小钱，我就让你来听我的直播，你长大之后会恨我的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 50,
      "start": 3592.284,
      "end": 3592.296,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你会长大的，对吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 51,
      "start": 3592.296,
      "end": 3592.313,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你长大之后一定会恨我的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 52,
      "start": 3592.332,
      "end": 3592.347,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你会想当年遇见个什么东西。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 53,
      "start": 3592.355,
      "end": 3592.385,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以我一直拒绝，我一直拒绝学生来听我的直播。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 54,
      "start": 3592.385,
      "end": 3592.427,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "偶尔搭听了一点点有趣的知识就行了，但是更多时候其实是应该让孩子自己去读书的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 55,
      "start": 3592.435,
      "end": 3592.463,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后呢，我后来又跟他们说，如果你爸妈需要买一点菜，对吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 56,
      "start": 3592.463,
      "end": 3592.494,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "爸妈需要买点菜你可以来，但请你自己不要来。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 57,
      "start": 3592.494,
      "end": 3592.512,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "也不要整天在我这讲听。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 58,
      "start": 3592.512,
      "end": 3592.536,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我其实讲的也并不深入，也并不完整。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 59,
      "start": 3592.536,
      "end": 3592.553,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "可能甚至有时是一种泛知识。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 60,
      "start": 3592.553,
      "end": 3592.563,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "对吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 61,
      "start": 3592.563,
      "end": 3592.599,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "是极其夹杂着极其强烈的个人情感的知识。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 62,
      "start": 3593.0,
      "end": 3593.053,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我也特别希望有一天你拿着杜甫传，拿着苏东坡传，拿着李白传，可以解读出极其具有自己强烈的一个。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 63,
      "start": 3593.053,
      "end": 3593.102,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但你要知道董宇辉可不是一直在镜头前，在这直播把那知识播出来的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 64,
      "start": 3593.102,
      "end": 3593.176,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "董宇辉是在漫长的失眠的夜里头，实在睡不着觉，洗完了衣服，拖完了地，实在没事干，坐在这去看纪录片，研究史料研究出来的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 65,
      "start": 3593.18,
      "end": 3593.236,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果没有那些时间，我长期的阅读和修炼，我不可能现在在屏幕前给你啰啰嗦嗦的胡说八道。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 66,
      "start": 3593.24,
      "end": 3593.254,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有的确实是胡说八道。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 67,
      "start": 3593.254,
      "end": 3593.264,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "不一定对。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 68,
      "start": 3593.264,
      "end": 3593.285,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以我知道屏幕前有孩子。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 69,
      "start": 3593.285,
      "end": 3593.303,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以我必须今天把这段话说给你。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 70,
      "start": 3593.303,
      "end": 3593.334,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我也不知道为什么刚才就从一个牛的品种说到了农业。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 71,
      "start": 3593.334,
      "end": 3593.362,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "说到了年轻人应该去寻找自己的使命。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
