    {
      "idx": 149,
      "start": 3596.524,
      "end": 3596.534,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "OK。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 150,
      "start": 3596.534,
      "end": 3596.575,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就是平常是有那个信息，但最近一段时间导演不给我反评，因为我每天也不读呢。",
