      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 151,
      "start": 3596.575,
      "end": 3596.596,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我在这胡写小作文，胡讲人生经历。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 152,
      "start": 3596.596,
      "end": 3597.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "导演生气了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 153,
      "start": 3597.014,
      "end": 3597.028,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "想要的朋友自己去拍啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 154,
      "start": 3597.038,
      "end": 3597.078,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我会进步的，这两天有很多朋友私信已经提醒了，董宇辉你是个卖货主播，请你做好自己的工作职责。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 155,
      "start": 3597.087,
      "end": 3597.127,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我觉得很庆幸就是生活中一些经历，有一些朋友去提醒你，而不是一味的去赞同你。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 156,
      "start": 3597.133,
      "end": 3597.176,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "敢于在你骄傲的时候泼冷水的人。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 157,
      "start": 3597.185,
      "end": 3597.207,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他们往往可能也是真的在关心你啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 158,
      "start": 3597.216,
      "end": 3597.228,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "功课，想要自己去拍啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 159,
      "start": 3597.228,
      "end": 3597.254,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "来，接下来一个是这个宁夏的滩羊肉。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 160,
      "start": 3597.254,
      "end": 3597.266,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "这个有多少个啊，导演？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 161,
      "start": 3597.275,
      "end": 3597.284,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "还有500单。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 162,
      "start": 3597.284,
      "end": 3597.294,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "还有500单。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 163,
      "start": 3597.294,
      "end": 3597.305,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那很快。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 164,
      "start": 3597.305,
      "end": 3597.316,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "咱现在直播间里30万人呢。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 165,
      "start": 3597.324,
      "end": 3597.33,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "500。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 166,
      "start": 3597.337,
      "end": 3597.347,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "宁夏的滩羊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 167,
      "start": 3597.347,
      "end": 3597.364,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我不知道大家喜欢去西北吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 168,
      "start": 3597.364,
      "end": 3597.389,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果你喜欢去西北啊，你其实从西安出发是非常好的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 169,
      "start": 3597.394,
      "end": 3597.425,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "从西安出发，你晚上可以到，开到或者四个小时。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 170,
      "start": 3597.425,
      "end": 3597.435,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "都不用晚上。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 171,
      "start": 3597.435,
      "end": 3597.455,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你可以在这个延安停上一天。",
