      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 172,
      "start": 3597.464,
      "end": 3597.478,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后你去一下宝塔山。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 173,
      "start": 3597.485,
      "end": 3597.519,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "其实延安有一个特殊的擀面皮，它是那种黑色粗两做的，很好吃。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 174,
      "start": 3597.519,
      "end": 3597.535,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后你可以去延安停上一天。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 175,
      "start": 3597.535,
      "end": 3597.555,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后在延安住一天，第二天再往宁夏去走。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 176,
      "start": 3597.555,
      "end": 3598.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "到了宁夏呢，大家就知道有一个非常经典的叫叫老毛家还是啥。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 177,
      "start": 3598.0,
      "end": 3598.014,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我记得我去吃过好几次。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 178,
      "start": 3598.014,
      "end": 3598.025,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但我记不住名字。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 179,
      "start": 3598.025,
      "end": 3598.043,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他们就那个手手抓肉。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 180,
      "start": 3598.043,
      "end": 3598.062,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后泡那个八宝茶。",
      "text_normalized": "",
