      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "反正老马手抓。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 187,
      "start": 3598.198,
      "end": 3598.205,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "反正我是去过的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 188,
      "start": 3598.205,
      "end": 3598.234,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以我记得当时去吃那个手抓肉的时候就特别的畅快。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 189,
      "start": 3598.234,
      "end": 3598.256,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "因为那天我是一大早从西安出发。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 190,
      "start": 3598.256,
      "end": 3598.267,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我中间没有停。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 191,
      "start": 3598.267,
      "end": 3598.277,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我开了一路。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 192,
      "start": 3598.294,
      "end": 3598.314,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "一路就听着一生所爱嘛。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 193,
      "start": 3598.314,
      "end": 3598.327,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我每次去都一路听一生所爱。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 194,
      "start": 3598.327,
      "end": 3598.336,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后开了一路。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 195,
      "start": 3598.336,
      "end": 3598.346,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后饥肠辘辘。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 196,
      "start": 3598.346,
      "end": 3598.374,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "到那块之后有一个以前去过的朋友跟我推荐，让我直接去找那家店。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 197,
      "start": 3598.374,
      "end": 3598.414,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我到那家店之后，你就点了一大盘肉，然后泡了个茶。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 198,
      "start": 3598.414,
      "end": 3598.459,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你知道饥肠辘辘的一个女人啊，她需要的就是一顿这个饱餐。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 199,
      "start": 3598.463,
      "end": 3598.484,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后呢，喝着那个茶，吃着那个肉。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 200,
      "start": 3598.484,
      "end": 3598.53,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那个好像离当地他们的那个钟楼还是鼓楼很近，我记得就在旁边好像是。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 201,
      "start": 3598.53,
      "end": 3598.544,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "哇，吃完之后特别舒服。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 202,
      "start": 3598.544,
      "end": 3598.555,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "太爽了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 203,
      "start": 3598.574,
      "end": 3599.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "这个宁夏的滩羊是因为它在黄河滩上。",
