      "text": "就是河套平原的西套。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 205,
      "start": 3599.022,
      "end": 3599.055,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "它是盐碱地，所以盐碱中和之后，羊肉没有腥膻味。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 206,
      "start": 3599.07,
      "end": 3599.083,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我特别喜欢那个地方。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 207,
      "start": 3599.083,
      "end": 3599.095,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "确实有古楼是吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 208,
      "start": 3599.095,
      "end": 3599.144,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "昨天也有朋友一直在给我提出建议，说董宇辉你不要在直播的时候一直摸鼻子，这样显得对观众不尊重。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 209,
      "start": 3599.144,
      "end": 3599.166,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我对不起啊，我是因为镜头前有强光。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 210,
      "start": 3599.166,
      "end": 3599.187,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "照射之后我眼睛和鼻子一直痒。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 211,
      "start": 3599.187,
      "end": 3599.196,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有时候可能是无意识的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 212,
      "start": 3599.196,
      "end": 3599.205,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我今天尽量控制。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 213,
      "start": 3599.205,
      "end": 3599.213,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 214,
      "start": 3599.259,
      "end": 3599.277,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你可以给大家再放一个一生所爱吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 215,
      "start": 3599.277,
      "end": 3599.287,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有朋友要听，可以吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 216,
      "start": 3599.287,
      "end": 3599.294,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "可以。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 217,
      "start": 3599.294,
      "end": 3599.306,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "可以，谢谢啊，谢谢。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 218,
      "start": 3599.324,
      "end": 3599.352,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "每次去宁夏的路上，我其实都不怎么说话啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 219,
      "start": 3599.352,
      "end": 3599.367,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "因为一路在听这个嘛，对吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 220,
      "start": 3599.367,
      "end": 3599.387,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就像我跟大家说的，人生其实很多时候讲出来就是很多遗憾。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 221,
      "start": 3599.387,
      "end": 3599.434,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我们那天晚上再给大家讲到这个大话西游的时候，就提到了这个。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 3
    },
    {
      "idx": 222,
      "start": 3599.444,
